{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_53_01",
  "title": "兵藤雫 1話 これは家宝にしなきゃ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――十月十五日　朝",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依さん、その年代のアイドルが好きだったんですね\n実力派揃いで、凄くいい時代……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ。母の影響で、小さい頃から観ていたの\nもっと昔のアイドルも知っているわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "いつか、そういう先輩達が青春を燃やして歌った歌を\n私もカバーしてみたいなって思っているくらい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "おぉ……！　瑠依さん、意外とアイドルオタク\n昔のアイドルが好きなら、遙子さんとも話が合うかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、今度話してみようかしら。って、ごめんなさい\n雫の誕生日なのに、自分の話ばかりしているわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことない。瑠依さんとアイドルの話が出来るの\n凄く嬉しい、です……！　グッズとかは持ってますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "CDくらいかしら。でも、一度飾ったりしてみたいわね\nファンの人達の気持ちが、より分かりそうだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "なら今から体験してみましょう……！\n学校までまだ時間あるし、グッズとケース、用意する！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4130.995972999997,
          "startTime": 70.030995973
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4333.33333329999,
          "startTime": 70.2333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.0999979655
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.0999979655
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "アクリルスタンドに、缶バッジ……。私のグッズが\nこんなに沢山……。というか、自分のグッズを飾るのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.4333302816
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "……ハッ！　確かに、つい瑠依さんのグッズを\n選んじゃった。別の子のが良ければ、そこに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.4999933879
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、大丈夫よ。そのかわり、せっかくだし完成したら\n雫の部屋に、このケースを飾ってもらおうかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.7666554769
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "飾る！　飾ります！　瑠依さんにグッズケースを作って\nもらえるなんて嬉し過ぎる！　凄い誕生日になってきた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8866.666666699999,
          "startTime": 109.8666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11666.666666699995,
          "startTime": 112.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.2333241779
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "といっても、こういうの初めてなんだけど\nとりあえず一つ……こうかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.8333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7000,
          "startTime": 116.8333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.9666641235
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "床面に一つだけ缶バッジを置くなんて、斬新……\nただ、最初はもっとオーソドックスに作ってもいいかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.6999847413
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "っ……そ、そっか、基本は横から見るものなのね\nそれなら……あら？　これって、雫の……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.6333180746
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、なんでもないわ。見られていると恥ずかしいから\nプレゼントにあげた、おまんじゅうでも食べていて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.4666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14233.333333299981,
          "startTime": 159.7
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-close-01.m4a",
          "delay": 16099.999999999995,
          "startTime": 161.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ、出来た。それじゃあ、私はもう行くわね\n雫、貴重な経験をありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.4941922965,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.099987793
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.299971517
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依さん、作り終えたら、ささっと出て行っちゃった\nどうかしたのかな……。って、あれ？　これって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 177.5666585286
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_01-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "私のグッズ交ざっちゃってた！？　瑠依さんと並んでる\nなんだか照れちゃうけど……これは家宝にしなきゃ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
